        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Distressed him, but strengthened him not - This statement, and that at the end of 2 Chronicles 28:21, is supplemental to, and not contradictory of, 2 Kings 16:9. Here it is the writer's object to note that the material assistance rendered by Tiglath-pileser to Ahab, was no real \"help\" or \"strength,\" but rather a cause of \"distress.\" ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "Distressed him, but strengthened him not - This statement, and that at the end of ",
